summary: An ordinance accepting deeds from Gunder Nielsen and others to a portion of the northwest one-quarter of the southeast one-quarter of Section 2, Township 23 North, Range 4 East, W. M., and other properties, for street purposes, and laying off 59th Avenue South, 41st Avenue Northeast, West Donovan Street, 1st Avenue Northeast, 7th Avenue Northeast, and 13th Avenue Northwest.
